24 Jul 2015 19:38






This is what happens when you have nothing to listen to in the car except Kingston Trio because your radio is broken. In all honesty, this was me seeing if I could stick a bunch of disparate elements together- a corrupted Kingston Trio song, characters from my UIU series (yes, I will get back to that eventually, for the half of a person who actually read that), spatial fuckery, and the swamp. Plus, don't tell me  isn't a cool word. You are lying.

Thanks to everyone who looked over this in chat. Enjoy!







